{
  "texts": [
    "We also evaluated the impact of various key parameters and compared their performance with that of domain experts.",
    "By fusing domain knowledge and chains of thought, we proposed an optimal prompt for in-context zero-shot learning and observed its favorable outcomes.",
    "We used the approach previously presented in,23 to prepare the dataset from MIMIC-III 24.",
    "More details can be found in Appendix A.",
    "As a result, we created a dataset that includes 1,873 discharge summaries with 178 patients with metastatic cancer."
  ]
}